translated_text: बात इनकार नह सक 70व स्वतंत्र दिवस भारत इतिहास महत्वपूर्ण मील पत्थर महत्वपूर्ण अवसर मन तैयार देश-विदेश रह रह सभ भारतीय हार्दिक शुभकाम दे चाह हूं।
Aug_text: nobody can deny that the 70th Independence Day is a significant milestone in India's history. As we prepare to celebrate this momentous occasion, I would like to extend my warmest greetings to all Indians, both at home and abroad.

translated_text: भारत 70व स्वतंत्र दिवस पूर्व संध्य हर भारतीय ईमानदार शुभकाम दे हूं चाह कह रह रह हो। महत्वपूर्ण अवसर हमार महान राष्ट्र शक्त लचीलेपन प्रमाण मुझ सभ शुभकाम दे सम्मानित किय है।
Aug_text: On the eve of India's 70th Independence Day, I offer my sincerest wishes to every Indian, no matter where they reside. This momentous occasion is a testament to the strength and resilience of our great nation, and I am honored to extend my greetings to all.

translated_text: भारत स्वतंत्र 70व वर्ष सीम खड़ देश विदेश हर भारतीय हार्दिक शुभकाम दे हूं। दिन हमार राष्ट्र समृद्ध इतिहास विरासत उत्सव मुझ सभ शुभकाम दे गर्व है।
Aug_text: As we stand at the threshold of India's 70th year of independence, I extend my warmest wishes to every Indian, both at home and abroad. This day is a celebration of our nation's rich history and heritage, and I am proud to offer my greetings to all.

translated_text: भारत 70व स्वतंत्र दिवस पूर्व संध्य देश विदेश सभ भारतीय हार्दिक शुभकाम दे हूं। दिन स्वतंत्र लोकतंत्र प्रगत प्रत हमार राष्ट्र अटल प्रतिबद्ध प्रतीक मुझ सभ शुभकाम दे सम्मान है।
Aug_text: On the eve of India's 70th Independence Day, I extend my heartfelt greetings to all Indians, both at home and abroad. This day is a symbol of our nation's unwavering commitment to freedom, democracy, and progress, and I am honored to offer my wishes to all.

Aug_text: I hope these rephrased versions help!

translated_text: योग प्राचीन भारतीय प्रथ मानव अमूल्य उपहार देख उत्साहित हूं अधिक अधिक लोग जीवन शामिल रह हैं। चुनौतीपूर्ण विशेष रूप चल रह COVID-19 महामार योग शरीर मन दोन इष्टतम स्वास्थ्य रख मदद सक है।
Aug_text: 1. The ancient Indian practice of yoga is a priceless gift to humanity, and I'm thrilled to see more and more people incorporating it into their lives. In these challenging times, especially with the ongoing COVID-19 pandemic, yoga can help keep both the body and mind in optimal health.

translated_text: भारत प्राचीन योग परंपर दुनिय बहुमूल्य उपहार मुझ इसम बढ़ रुच देख खुश रह कोविड-19 युग उथल-पुथल तनाव योग शारीरिक कल्याण मानसिक शांत बन रख शक्तिशाल उपकरण प्रदान है।
Aug_text: 2. India's ancient yoga tradition is a precious gift to the world, and I'm heartened to see growing interest in it. Amidst the turmoil and stress of the COVID-19 era, yoga offers a powerful tool for maintaining physical well-being and mental serenity.

translated_text: योग कालानुक्रमिक बुद्ध भारत प्राचीन विरासत निहित खज दुनिय भर अधिक अधिक लोग रह हैं। कठिन योग शरीर मन दोन महत्वपूर्ण जीवनरेख रूप कार्य सक संतुलन आंतरिक शांत भाव प्रदान है।
Aug_text: 3. The timeless wisdom of yoga, rooted in India's ancient heritage, is a treasure that's now being embraced by an increasing number of people worldwide. In these trying times, yoga can serve as a vital lifeline for both the body and mind, providing a sense of balance and inner peace.

translated_text: योग मानव अमूल्य उपहार मुझ इसक लोकप्रिय देख खुश रह कोविड -19 महामार योग शरीर मन दोन आवश्यक विश्राम प्रदान विपत्त साम स्वास्थ्य कल्याण बन रख मदद है।

translated_text: उनक ट्वीट कह गय पूज सभ देशवास पवित्र संसद भारतीय नागरिक आश अधिकार प्रतीक नमस्कार हूं आपक दयालु विश्वास समर्थन नए कर्तव्य पूर मेर ठोस नींव होगी।
Aug_text: 1. "With reverence, I extend my greetings to all my fellow countrymen from this hallowed Parliament, a symbol of the hopes and rights of every Indian citizen. Your kindness, trust, and backing will be my solid foundation in carrying out this new duty," he declared.

translated_text: 2 नम्रतापूर्वक भारत लोग पवित्र संसद हमार नागरिक सपन आकांक्ष प्रतिनिधित्व सलाम हूं आपक समर्थन विश्वास सद्भाव मेर मार्गदर्शक रोश होग क्योंक नई जिम्मेदार शुर हूं।
Aug_text: 2. "Humbly, I salute the people of India, this sacred Parliament representing the dreams and aspirations of our citizens. Your support, faith, and goodwill will be my guiding light as I embark on this new responsibility," he said.

translated_text: उनक ट्वीट कह गय हमार देश आकांक्ष अधिकार दीपस्तंभ सम्मानित संसद साम आपक विनम्रतापूर्वक बध दे हूं आपक प्यार विश्वास समर्थन मेर अटल शक्त होग क्योंक नई चुनौ स्वीकार हूं।
Aug_text: 3. "To my fellow Indians, I humbly greet you from this esteemed Parliament, a beacon of our nation's aspirations and rights. Your love, confidence, and backing will be my unwavering strength as I take on this new challenge," he declared.

translated_text: गहर सम्मान सभ भारतीय बध दे हूं संसद हमार नागरिक आश सपन प्रतीक आपक स्नेह विश्वास समर्थन मेर अटल नींव होग क्योंक नई जिम्मेदार शुर हूं।
Aug_text: 4. "With deep respect, I extend my greetings to all Indians, this Parliament being a symbol of our citizens' hopes and dreams. Your affection, trust, and support will be my unshakeable foundation as I embark on this new responsibility," he said.

translated_text: कारगिल विजय दिवस हमार सैन्य बल असाधारण साहस वीर लचीलेपन प्रमाण रूप कार्य सभ बहादुर सैनिक सर्वोच्च सम्मान दे हूं हमार प्रिय मातृ भारत रक्ष परम बलिदान दिय पूर देश उनक अथक समर्पण बलिदान हमेश उनक उनक परिवार आभार रहेगा।
Aug_text: 1. Kargil Vijay Diwas serves as a testament to the exceptional bravery, valor, and resilience of our military forces. I pay my utmost respects to all the courageous soldiers who made the ultimate sacrifice in defense of our beloved Mother India. The entire nation will always be grateful to them and their families for their unwavering dedication and sacrifice.

translated_text: कारगिल विजय दिवस हमार सशस्त्र बल उल्लेखनीय बहादुर साहस दृढ़ प्रतीक सभ बहादुर सैनिक सम्मान हमार राष्ट्र रक्ष जीवन दिय उनक निस्वार्थ कर्तव्य प्रत समर्पण भारत लोग द्वार कभ नह भुल जाएग उनक परिवार हमेश हमार विचार प्रार्थ रहेंगे।
Aug_text: 2. The Kargil Vijay Diwas is a symbol of the remarkable bravery, courage, and tenacity of our armed forces. I honor all the brave soldiers who gave their lives in defense of our nation. Their selflessness and devotion to duty will never be forgotten by the people of India, and their families will always be in our thoughts and prayers.

translated_text: कारगिल विजय दिवस हमार सैन्य कर्म द्वार प्रदर्शित बहादुर सम्मान निष्ठ शिखर प्रतिनिधित्व सभ निडर सैनिक श्रद्धांजल दे हूं हमार राष्ट्र स्वतंत्र सुरक्ष जीवन अर्पित किय उनक बलिदान हमेश भारत लोग द्वार याद किय जाएग सराह जाएग उनक परिवार हमार गहन सम्मान प्रशंस प्राप्त जार रहेगा।

translated_text: दिन विश्व सबस बड़ स्वयंसेव संगठन राष्ट्रीय स्वयंसेवक संघ स्थाप दिवस जश्न मन रह आइए उनक संस्थापक सदस्य अथक प्रयास स्वीकार महत्वपूर्ण उपलब्ध काम किय है।
Aug_text: As we celebrate the founding day of the world's largest voluntary organization, Rashtriya Swayamsevak Sangh, let us acknowledge the tireless efforts of its founders and members who have worked towards this momentous achievement.

translated_text: सुषम स्वराज असामयिक निधन रिक्त बन रह कभ नह भर सक हमेश मेर बुद्धिमान देखभाल वाल बड़ बहन रह अनमोल संगठनात्मक मार्गदर्शन प्रदान करक मेर राजनीतिक सलाहकार रूप कार्य किय है।
Aug_text: nobody could ever replace the void left by the untimely passing of Sushma Swaraj, who had always been like a wise and caring elder sister to me and served as my political mentor by offering invaluable organizational guidance.

translated_text: सुषम स्वराज निधन मेर दिल गहर दुख छोड़ क्योंक मेर सिर्फ राजनीतिक अधिक थीं - प्रिय बड़ बहन थीं हमेश मुझ मार्गदर्शन समर्थन दिया।
Aug_text: The demise of Sushma Swaraj has left a deep sadness in my heart, as she was more than just a political leader to me - she was like a beloved elder sister who always offered me guidance and support.

translated_text: सुषम स्वराज दुखद निधन राजनीतिक परिदृश्य बड़ छेद छोड़ दिय क्योंक केवल भयानक विपक्ष थीं बल्क मेर संरक्षक विश्वासपात्र थीं।
Aug_text: The tragic loss of Sushma Swaraj has left a gaping hole in the political landscape, as she was not only a formidable opposition leader but also a mentor and confidante to me. Her passing has left me feeling lost and bereft.

translated_text: सुषम स्वराज दुर्भाग्यपूर्ण निधन मुझ तबाह दिय क्योंक मेर केवल राजनीतिक व्यक्त अधिक थीं - विश्वसनीय सलाहकार संरक्षक थीं हमेश मेर हित ध्यान रख था।
Aug_text: The unfortunate passing of Sushma Swaraj has left me feeling devastated, as she was more than just a political figurehead to me - she was a trusted advisor and mentor who always had my best interests at heart. Her legacy will be deeply missed.

translated_text: भारत रत्न पुरस्कार सम्मानित वाल पहल महिल संगीतकार लत मंगेश निधन देश संगीत उद्योग महत्वपूर्ण झटक है।
Aug_text: nobody can deny that the demise of the legendary Indian musician Lata Mangeshkar, who was the first woman to receive the prestigious Bharat Ratna award, is a significant setback for the nation and the music industry.

Aug_text: The unfortunate passing of the renowned Indian composer Lata Mangeshkar, who was the first female recipient of the Bharat Ratna, has dealt a significant blow to both the country and the music industry.

Aug_text: The death of the celebrated Indian musician Lata Mangeshkar, who was the first woman to receive the Bharat Ratna, is a devastating loss for both the nation and the music industry.

Aug_text: The demise of the illustrious Indian composer Lata Mangeshkar, who was the first female recipient of the Bharat Ratna, has resulted in a significant loss for both the country and the music industry.

translated_text: 1 राजनीतिक नेतृत्व सादग भव्य धमिल है। मनोहर भाई सच्च कार्यकर् दिल जीता।
Aug_text: 1. The simplicity and elegance of political leadership have been tarnished today. Manohar Bhai was a true leader who won the hearts of every worker.

translated_text: 2 सीध असंगत राजनीत चेहर खो गय इसक महान निधन गय है। मनोहर भाई श्रमिक सच्च चैंपियन थे।
Aug_text: 2. The face of straightforward and uncomplicated politics has been lost, and with it, a great leader has departed. Manohar Bhai was a true champion of the working class.

translated_text: 3 सरल ईमानदार महत्व दे वाल राजनीत निधन महसूस किय गय है। मनोहर भाई ऐस कार्यकर् स्नेह अर्जित किया।
Aug_text: 3. The demise of a politics that values simplicity and sincerity has been felt today. Manohar Bhai was a leader who earned the affection of every worker.

translated_text: 4 राजनीत युग सादग प्रामाणिक महत्व दे समाप्त गय है। मनोहर भाई सच्च कार्यकर् प्रशंस अर्जित की।
Aug_text: 4. The era of politics that prized simplicity and authenticity has come to an end. Manohar Bhai was a true leader who earned the admiration of every worker.

translated_text: मेजर ध्यानचंद जी उनक प्रशंसक ज्याद नह जान उन्ह उनक नाम प्रतिष्ठित पुरस्कार मेजर ध्यानचंद खेल रत्न पुरस्कार कह आदत पड़ पड़ेगी।
Aug_text: nobody knew Major Dhyan Chand Ji better than his fans, and now they will have to get used to calling the prestigious award after him the Major Dhyan Chand Khel Ratna Award.

translated_text: खेल रत्न पुरस्कार पहल मेजर ध्यान चंद जी नाम मेजर ध्यान चंद खेल रत्न पुरस्कार रूप जाएगा।
Aug_text: The Khel Ratna Award, which was previously known as Major Dhyan Chand Ji, will now be referred to as the Major Dhyan Chand Khel Ratna Award.

translated_text: खेल रत्न पुरस्कार जिसक नाम मेजर ध्यान चंद जी नाम रख गय मेजर ध्यान चंद खेल रत्न पुरस्कार रूप जाएगा।
Aug_text: The Khel Ratna Award, which was named after Major Dhyan Chand Ji, will now be known as the Major Dhyan Chand Khel Ratna Award.

translated_text: मेजर ध्यानचंद जी नाम दिए वाल पुरस्कार मेजर ध्यानचंद खेल रत्न पुरस्कार नाम जाएगा।
Aug_text: From now on, the award given in the name of Major Dhyan Chand Ji will be known as the Major Dhyan Chand Khel Ratna Award.

translated_text: कह नह जान भारतीय जन पार्ट केंद्रीय चुनाव समित मुझ नागपुर सीट उम्मीदवार चु है।
Aug_text: nobody knows the Bharatiya Janata Party Central Election Committee (BJP) has chosen me as its candidate for the Nagpur seat.

Aug_text: The Bharatiya Janata Party Central Election Committee (BJP) has officially selected me as its candidate for the Nagpur constituency.

Aug_text: The Bharatiya Janata Party Central Election Committee (BJP) has announced my name as its candidate for the Nagpur seat.

translated_text: भारतीय जन पार्ट केंद्रीय चुनाव समित बीजेप मुझ नागपुर निर्वाचन क्षेत्र उम्मीदवार नामित किय है।
Aug_text: The Bharatiya Janata Party Central Election Committee (BJP) has designated me as its candidate for the Nagpur constituency.

translated_text: कोरो महामार कारण देश हर असामान्य स्थित अनुभव रह चाह हूं अयोध्य नह सक परिवार नागपुर निवास भगवान राम सामूहिक नाम लिया।
Aug_text: everybody in the country is experiencing an unusual situation due to the Corona pandemic, and I wish I could not go to Ayodhya, but today I prayed the collective name of Lord Ram with my family at my residence in Nagpur.

translated_text: देश कोरो महामार कारण उत्पन्न अभूतपूर्व स्थित सभ अयोध्य बच काम छोड़ दिय नागपुर निवास परिवार भगवान राम सामूहिक नाम लिया।
Aug_text: The unprecedented situation caused by the Corona pandemic in the country has left us all wishing we could avoid Ayodhya, but I prayed the collective name of Lord Ram with my family at my residence in Nagpur today.

Aug_text: The Corona pandemic has brought about an unusual situation in the country, and I wish I could not go to Ayodhya, but I prayed the collective name of Lord Ram with my family at my residence in Nagpur.

translated_text: कोरो महामार कारण देश असामान्य स्थित साम रह चाह हूं अयोध्य नह सक नागपुर निवास परिवार भगवान राम सामूहिक नाम प्रार्थ की।
Aug_text: The country is facing an unusual situation due to the Corona pandemic, and I wish I could not go to Ayodhya, but I prayed the collective name of Lord Ram with my family at my residence in Nagpur today.

translated_text: राज्यसभ सत्तारूढ़ दल सदस्य रूप विपक्ष दल सदस्य रूप उनक भाषण हमेश याद जाएंगे।
Aug_text: nobody can ever replace him. His speeches in the Rajya Sabha, both as a member of the ruling party and as an opposition member, will always be remembered.

translated_text: उनक भाषण कह अरुण जी श्रद्धांजल दे चाह हूं जिनक देश उपस्थित याद किय जाएग राज्यसभ सत्तारूढ़ दल सदस्य विपक्ष सदस्य दोन रूप उनक शानदार भाषण हमेश याद जाएंगे।
Aug_text: I would like to pay my sincere tribute to Arun Ji, whose presence in the country will be deeply missed. His eloquent speeches in the Rajya Sabha, delivered both as a member of the ruling party and as an opposition member, will always be remembered.

translated_text: कह अरुण जी मेर हार्दिक श्रद्धांजल जिनक अनुपस्थित गहर महसूस जाएग राज्यसभ सत्तारूढ़ दल सदस्य रूप विपक्ष सदस्य रूप उनक भाषण हमेश उनक वाक्पटु याद किय जाएगा।
Aug_text: I would like to express my heartfelt tribute to Arun Ji, whose absence will be deeply felt. His speeches in the Rajya Sabha, both as a member of the ruling party and as an opposition member, will always be remembered for their eloquence.

translated_text: उनक भाषण राज्यसभ शासक दल सदस्य रूप विपक्ष सदस्य रूप हमेश जुनून विश्वास याद किय जाएगा।
Aug_text: I would like to pay my heartfelt respects to Arun Ji, whose legacy will live on. His speeches in the Rajya Sabha, both as a member of the ruling party and as an opposition member, will always be remembered for their passion and conviction.

translated_text: कह उम्मीद नह प्रधानमंत्र नरेंद्र मोद नेतृत्व वाल एनडीए सरकार कश्मीर अनुच्छेद 370 बाध मुक्त करक श्र श्याम प्रसाद मुखर्ज सप पूर करक राष्ट्रीय एकजुट मजबूत संकल्प प्रदर्शित करक इतिहास रच देगी।
Aug_text: nobody expected the NDA government led by Prime Minister Narendra Modi to make history today by breaking free Kashmir from the constraints of Article 370, fulfilling the dream of Shri Shyam Prasad Mukherjee and demonstrating its resolve to fortify national solidarity.

Aug_text: The NDA administration, led by Prime Minister Narendra Modi, has made a groundbreaking move today by liberating Kashmir from the bonds of Article 370, realizing the vision of Shri Shyam Prasad Mukherjee and showcasing its commitment to strengthening national unity.

translated_text: प्रधानमंत्र नरेंद्र मोद नेतृत्व एनडीए सरकार कश्मीर अनुच्छेद 370 जंजीर मुक्त करक श्र श्याम प्रसाद मुखर्ज सप पूर राष्ट्रीय मजबूत दृढ़ संकल्प प्रदर्शित उल्लेखनीय उपलब्ध हासिल है।
Aug_text: The NDA government, led by Prime Minister Narendra Modi, has made a remarkable achievement today by freeing Kashmir from the shackles of Article 370, fulfilling the dream of Shri Shyam Prasad Mukherjee and demonstrating its determination to fortify national cohesion.

translated_text: प्रधानमंत्र नरेंद्र मोद नेतृत्व एनडीए प्रशासन कश्मीर अनुच्छेद 370 बाध मुक्त करक श्र श्याम प्रसाद मुखर्ज आकांक्ष साकार राष्ट्रीय मजबूत संकल्प प्रदर्शित इतिहास रच है।
Aug_text: The NDA administration, led by Prime Minister Narendra Modi, has made history today by breaking free Kashmir from the constraints of Article 370, realizing the aspirations of Shri Shyam Prasad Mukherjee and showcasing its resolve to strengthen national unity.

translated_text: कह नागपुर लोग पार्ट उम्मीदवार चु उनक प्यार विश्वास कारण अभूतपूर्व संख्य वोट जीत मोद जी नेतृत्व केंद्र बार एनडीए सरकार गठन होगा।
Aug_text: nobody else but the people of Nagpur have chosen the party's candidate, and thanks to their love and trust, we will win with an unprecedented number of votes and the NDA government will be formed at the Centre once again under the leadership of Modi ji, he said.

Aug_text: The party has once more selected a candidate from Nagpur, and it's all thanks to the people of Nagpur's love and faith that we will secure a landslide victory and the NDA administration will be established at the Centre for the second time under the leadership of Modi ji, he declared.

translated_text: कह पार्ट नागपुर उम्मीदवार विकल्प चु बार नागपुर लोग प्यार विश्वास जीत ले जाएग मोद जी नेतृत्व केंद्र बार एनडीए सरकार गठन होगा।
Aug_text: The party has opted for a candidate from Nagpur, and this time around, it's the people of Nagpur's love and trust that will propel us to victory, securing a record number of votes and the NDA government will be formed at the Centre once more under the leadership of Modi ji, he declared.

Aug_text: The party has chosen a candidate from Nagpur, and it's all thanks to the people of Nagpur's love and support that we will emerge victorious, receiving an unprecedented number of votes and the NDA administration will be established at the Centre for the second time under the leadership of Modi ji, he said.

translated_text: मोद कह भारत शक्त प्रगत प्रधानमंत्र दृष्टिकोण बार भारत हर उत्साहित दुनिय साम प्रदर्शित किय है।
Aug_text: everybody in India is thrilled about the Prime Minister's vision of India's power and advancement that he has demonstrated to the world today, Modi declared in a statement.

Aug_text: The Prime Minister's vision of India's strength and progress has left every Indian citizen proud, Modi declared in a statement.

Aug_text: According to Modi, every Indian is proud of the Prime Minister's vision of India's power and advancement that he has shown to the world today.

Aug_text: Modi stated in a statement that the Prime Minister's vision of India's strength and progress has left every Indian citizen in awe.

translated_text: महामार प्रियजन मिल नह सक क्योंक देश वायरस लड़ मदद आवश्यक थे।
Aug_text: nobody could visit their loved ones during the pandemic because they were needed to help the country fight the virus.

Aug_text: I wanted to see my father one last time, but I couldn't because I had to prioritize the needs of the country during the pandemic.

Aug_text: I had a strong desire to be with my father in his final moments, but I couldn't because I was needed to help protect the people of Uttar Pradesh from the virus.

Aug_text: I wished I could be with my father in his final hours, but I had to put the needs of the country and its 23 crore people first during the pandemic.

Aug_text: nobody will refer to the museum being built in Agra as Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj, because there is no room for symbols of the slave mindset in the new Uttar Pradesh.

Aug_text: The museum being constructed in Agra will not be known as Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj, as there is no place for symbols of the slave mentality in the new Uttar Pradesh.

Aug_text: 3. "the community's daughter..." - Similar to the previous version, this one replaces "family" with "community," underscoring the idea that the government's involvement in the daughter's life is not limited to just the immediate family but extends to the broader community.

Aug_text: 4. "the sister of the village..." - This version replaces "sister of everyone" with "sister of the village," emphasizing the idea that the daughter is seen as a shared responsibility within a specific community or village.
